arStrings.szText: Sacrifices made in life may protect loved ones in death.

Abasi, an aging warrior, wishes to perform an ancient Teganze ritual to protect his family after his death. His daughter, Jiona, fears his heart has outmatched his sense.

I should help Abasi find the Dahmu Blossoms he desires before he endangers himself in haste.
Collect Dahmu Blossoms from the Seram Trails ({DONE}/{NEEDED})
Bring the Dahmu Blossoms to Abasi
